				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BA%A1ch-ti%E1%BB%83u/poem-OCO5C4um2xdP3aPD_OYJEQ">Bạch tiểu - 白小</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-L%E1%BB%99-c%E1%BA%A9u-kh%E1%BA%A9u/poem-MdY3wD5w5oTiHWU_5wt-Sg">Khổng Lộ cẩu khẩu - 空路苟口</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/Ngu-m%E1%BB%B9-nh%C3%A2n-th%E1%BA%A3o-h%C3%A0nh/poem-N6O2IGtXnrrxjeKqu1KwiQ">Ngu mỹ nhân thảo hành - 虞美人草行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ngu%E1%BB%B5-Ngo%E1%BA%A1n/author-uWWMt6j8c6UoM1tDLnF61Q">Nguỵ Ngoạn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/Qu%C3%A1-Th%C3%A1nh-Qu%C3%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-UaeAJarCM1MsQDdHCNPCBg">Quá Thánh Quán tự - 大聖觀寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/author-6RHyKOpqR_VZ_nmIcRKQxw">Trần Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/T%E1%BA%A1p-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-eQq-ZMWyGeFY-eRWiRKWOQ">Tạp thi kỳ 1 - 雜詩其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Thanh-thanh-h%C3%A0-b%E1%BA%A1n-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-jNid850fZ_vreV9ycc8-Ig">Thanh thanh hà bạn thảo - 青青河畔草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/Tr%C3%BAc-T%C3%A2y-xu%C3%A2n-du-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-9RxHbi7DIjPJEHuci0MgKg">Trúc Tây xuân du khúc kỳ 1 - 竹西春遊曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/author-AwmtxAvU68PUawMGR0lmaw">Ngô Ỷ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-Chi%E1%BA%BFm-Mai/%E1%BB%A8c-t%C3%ADch/poem-xjVNXSKgaiD21dYg3VRC6g">Ức tích - 憶昔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-Chi%E1%BA%BFm-Mai/author-KcW-7-TuArU6v2a0Re1ZdQ">Lâm Chiếm Mai</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Vi%E1%BB%85n-bi%E1%BB%87t-ly/poem-chqUZSmoUmFAaHEcI_GANA">Viễn biệt ly - 遠別離</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-H%C3%A0n-T%C3%ADn/poem-P95BiLS0l9eMLlagLmHoOw">Vịnh sử - Hàn Tín - 詠史－韓信</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Ng%C3%B4-S%C3%B4/author-U-Qw0U7nLVKqm8kibmDN6g">Hà Ngô Sô</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
